#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:21
msgid ""
"Introduces runtime version compatibility metadata and checks across "
"Flower runtime components. AppIo communication for `flwr-serverapp`, "
"`flwr-simulation`, and `flwr-clientapp` now enforces matching "
"`major.minor` Flower releases, which prevents incompatible app runtime "
"combinations from proceeding. Control API and Fleet API also observe "
"runtime version metadata to prepare these paths for stricter "
"compatibility handling in future releases."
