#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:247
msgid ""
"Changes Flower CLI (`flwr`) configuration to introduce a new way to "
"manage SuperLink connections and simulation settings in a central place "
"(instead of Flower app's `pyproject.toml`). This enables `flwr` commands "
"to be executed from any directory and allow reuse of named connections "
"across different Flower apps. This change also removes the now obsolete "
"`enable-account-auth` option. The central Flower CLI config fully "
"replaces the legacy `federation` configuration in `pyproject.toml`, which"
" is automatically migrated to the new Flower configuration format when "
"running `flwr` commands. For usage details, see the [Flower CLI "
"reference](https://flower.ai/docs/framework/v1.26.0/en/ref-api-cli.html) "
"and the [Flower configuration "
"documentation](https://flower.ai/docs/framework/v1.26.0/en/ref-flower-"
"configuration.html)."
msgstr ""

